Class AsyncAutoCompleteHandler<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.yandex.subtitles.utils.AsyncAutoCompleteHandler<E>

  • public class AsyncAutoCompleteHandler<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    Class enqueues an action to be performed on a different thread than your own. Messages queue will be automatically stopped after specified timeout.
